                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-130-off682 t18281204-130-crimeloc685"></join>. About a quarter after nine o'clock on the evening of the 21st of November, I was in my little room, and heard somebody in the shop; I turned, and saw the prisoner run out with something in his apron- I ran and overtook him in a minute, with a piece of bacon in his apron; I had seen it safe five minutes before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281204-130-person1127">
